{"tid":1039434,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"如果你被困係自己間房，你可以忍受幾耐？","createTime":"2019-02-27T11:48:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-27T13:09:51.000Z","uid":56626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"cc82fba6fa94f78c92fdcb07fd17a930e291ad84","tid":1039434,"uid":56626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T11:48:46.000Z","msg":"假如你間房入面有充足食物，所有嘢就維持原狀，但係無得上網，你覺得你可以捱幾耐先悶到癲咗或者孤獨到想死？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我間房有唔少做手工嘅材料，又有啲書未睇，真係頂唔順仲可以研究下本古文觀止<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我估我應該頂多撐到一個月<br />\n<br />\n無房既巴絲向你地講聲對唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ed2ed4c67b1126f916e1ac50b654c7feef1723e","tid":1039434,"uid":46801,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T11:50:12.000Z","msg":"D屎尿 點算"},{"pid":"2784c5f71c5fa5f854f6c84cf06978836b0ac468","tid":1039434,"uid":231293,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T11:51:32.000Z","msg":"無上網咪用wifi囉😂😂on9<br />\n<br />\n一年都得"},{"pid":"a4d82137d71209550e0876b05c8d0f183bdc766d","tid":1039434,"uid":97855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T11:55:39.000Z","msg":"房有遊戲機有電視，幾個月唔難"},{"pid":"2829a6bb65b5fa1ec8c4f31fae5d9053d5014511","tid":1039434,"uid":148185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T11:59:00.000Z","msg":"兩日<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"947e057b06ed6750992721b27f91f5a02d868f3c","tid":1039434,"uid":56626,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5ed2ed4c67b1126f916e1ac50b654c7feef1723e","tid":1039434,"uid":46801,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T11:50:12.000Z","msg":"D屎尿 點算"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T12:01:33.000Z","msg":"假設你每日都屙完裝係膠袋掉出街<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0e42d63cabade292b5288818e087f0a24a1bdb0","tid":1039434,"uid":32691,"like":